          <p>
            I originally had a 10% VA disability rating and honestly felt stuck trying to figure out how to move forward. After working with Veterans Disability Network, their team helped me better organize my records, understand the claims process, and prepare the proper supporting documentation. In just six months, my rating increased from 10% to 90%. The professionalism, communication, and support I received from VDN made a tremendous difference for me and my family. You can tell they really care about Veterans and truly want to help you succeed.
          </p>
        </div>
        <footer class="tcard-foot">
          <div class="tcard-author">
            <h3 class="tcard-name">Daniel R. (Ret.)</h3>
            <span class="tcard-branch">U.S. Army</span>
            <span class="tcard-status-badge increased">Increased Benefits</span>
          </div>
